00:41:47,300 --> 00:41:49,140
 kad nemaju stručnog učitelja.

1191
00:41:49,140 --> 00:41:50,860
 A djeca su nam nepismena.

1192
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:51,880
 Evo vam rezultate,

1193
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:52,580
 evo, ja ne govorim,

1194
00:41:52,640 --> 00:41:53,000
 izmišljam,

1195
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:54,000
 pa je počitajte medije.

1196
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:55,880
 Rezultate nacionalnih matura.

1197
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,240
 Djeca ne znaju šta znači

1198
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:59,080
 ona požrtvovno sreće.

1199
00:41:59,080 --> 00:41:59,720
 O čemu mi prije...

1200
00:41:59,720 --> 00:42:00,600
 Ne čitaju knjige.

1201
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:01,800
 Ne čitaju lektire.

1202
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,260
 Ne čitaju knjige.

1203
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:02,840
 Ma ništa,

1204
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:04,220
 njima je sve to bez zveza.

1205
00:42:04,220 --> 00:42:04,740
 Njima je to...

1206
00:42:04,740 --> 00:42:05,780
 Zato što lektire,

1207
00:42:05,780 --> 00:42:06,620
 evo, recimo to,

1208
00:42:06,620 --> 00:42:07,860
 lektire se može dobiti

1209
00:42:07,860 --> 00:42:09,000
 sve nešto ovaj,

1210
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:10,400
 na A4 ili...

1211
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,240
 Ma može vam neko

1212
00:42:11,240 --> 00:42:12,960
 i doktorat napisati, evo.

1213
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,720
 Platite i napišu vam doktorat.

1214
00:42:14,720 --> 00:42:15,620
 Tako je seminar.

1215
00:42:15,740 --> 00:42:16,980
 Ma ljudi opće ne kuže

1216
00:42:16,980 --> 00:42:18,140
 šta gube zapravo time.

1217
00:42:18,140 --> 00:42:18,960
 Tako da...

1218
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,120
 U biti, ne vidio da je

1219
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:20,680
 proces...

1220
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:22,300
 Da je u tom procesu

1221
00:42:22,300 --> 00:42:24,000
 uživanje u tom radu

1222
00:42:24,000 --> 00:42:25,320
 da je to cilj.

1223
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:28,080
 Da nije stvar doći do nečega,

1224
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:28,960
 doći do diploma.

1225
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:29,560
 I što onda...

1226
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:31,140
 Oni stalo gledaju stramputicama,

1227
00:42:31,140 --> 00:42:33,020
 lakšim putem doći do rezultata.

1228
00:42:33,020 --> 00:42:34,640
 Ali ima jedna čuvena rečenica

1229
00:42:34,640 --> 00:42:36,460
 koju ja svojim učenicima često kažem.

1230
00:42:36,460 --> 00:42:37,120
 Dragi moji,

1231
00:42:37,120 --> 00:42:38,060
 vi stalo mi govorite

1232
00:42:38,060 --> 00:42:39,620
 kako sam ja vama dobar učitelj,

1233
00:42:39,620 --> 00:42:41,860
 kako vam širim veliko znanje o geografiji.

1234
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:42,800
 Ja sad vama kažem,

1235
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:44,840
 se zamislite na fakultetu,

1236
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,420
 da sam ja prepisivao i varao.

1237
00:42:46,420 --> 00:42:48,800
 I vi mene pitate,

1238
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,400
 profesor, možete vi nama objasniti

1239
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:51,580
 zašto Riže ima najviše

1240
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,440
 u jugoistočnoj Evropi?

1241
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,540
 A ja znam da sam taj dio

1242
00:42:53,540 --> 00:42:56,120
 ispita prepisao u jugoistočnu Aziju.

1243
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:57,080
 I ja kažem,

1244
00:42:57,080 --> 00:42:59,360
 pa istražite doma, evo.

1245
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:00,520
 Kažu oni,

1246
00:43:00,520 --> 00:43:02,260
 pa kako vi to morate...

1247
00:43:02,260 --> 00:43:03,640
 A šta da sam ja imao mogućnost,

1248
00:43:03,640 --> 00:43:04,520
 imao sam geografiju

1249
00:43:04,520 --> 00:43:05,280
 jugoistočnoj Evropi,

1250
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:06,520
 da sam to prepisao,

1251
00:43:06,520 --> 00:43:08,020
 da sam imao šalabakter,

1252
00:43:08,500 --> 00:43:09,880
 i on nišću ne bi znao o tome.

1253
00:43:09,880 --> 00:43:11,000
 Pa da,

1254
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:12,240
 kad izbunim,

1255
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,120
 on znači oni ne znaju šta,

1256
00:43:13,120 --> 00:43:13,880
 oni pocrvene,

1257
00:43:13,880 --> 00:43:15,320
 on poče im se pijeniti onako.

1258
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:16,700
 Znači, to je to.

1259
00:43:16,700 --> 00:43:18,660
 U biti treba stavljati izazove.

1260
00:43:18,660 --> 00:43:19,260
 To je to.

1261
00:43:19,260 --> 00:43:20,800
 Izazove, jako izazove.

1262
00:43:20,800 --> 00:43:22,200
 Da oni osijete,

1263
00:43:22,200 --> 00:43:23,700
 da moraju razmišljati,

1264
00:43:23,700 --> 00:43:24,280
 konstruktivno razmišljenje.

1265
00:43:24,280 --> 00:43:24,900
 Ja sam njima rekao,

1266
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:26,220
 ja ću rađe past ispit

1267
00:43:26,220 --> 00:43:27,140
 i naučit,

1268
00:43:27,140 --> 00:43:28,980
 jer znam da će to znanje

1269
00:43:28,980 --> 00:43:30,840
 nekad doći isplatit se.

1270
00:43:30,840 --> 00:43:32,260
 I to je sigurnost.

1271
00:43:32,260 --> 00:43:34,180
 Rupe koje dobijete

1272
00:43:34,180 --> 00:43:35,440
 kroz život gdje ste varali,

1273
00:43:35,440 --> 00:43:37,100
 morat ćete kad tad popuniti.

1274
00:43:37,100 --> 00:43:38,320
 Samo možda će biti kasno.

1275
00:43:38,320 --> 00:43:39,580
 I možda ćete izgubiti

1276
00:43:39,580 --> 00:43:40,660
 velike stvari u životu

1277
00:43:40,660 --> 00:43:41,460
 zbog jedne rupe

1278
00:43:41,460 --> 00:43:43,080
 koju ste samo inicijativno,

1279
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:44,240
 a mogli ste ju popuniti

1280
00:43:44,240 --> 00:43:45,420
 u mladim danima.

1281
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:46,020
 Tako da,

1282
00:43:46,020 --> 00:43:47,180
 sve se vrati,

1283
00:43:47,180 --> 00:43:48,200
 vjerujte mi u životu.

1284
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:49,200
 Svaka prevara,

1285
00:43:49,200 --> 00:43:50,040
 tako i

1286
00:43:50,040 --> 00:43:52,160
 gdje ste mislili

1287
00:43:52,160 --> 00:43:53,140
 stramputicom.

1288
00:43:54,580 --> 00:43:56,600
 Evo, ako ima pitanja

1289
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:59,420
 možete nas nazvati

1290
00:43:59,420 --> 00:44:05,420
 na 012327777.

1291
00:44:05,420 --> 00:44:07,280
 Evo, ponavljam još jedan put,

1292
00:44:07,280 --> 00:44:11,780
 012327777.

1293
00:44:11,780 --> 00:44:14,240
 Evo, profesor Dejan će rado odgovoriti.

1294
00:44:14,240 --> 00:44:15,520
 Neću ocjene djeliti.

1295
00:44:15,520 --> 00:44:16,620
 Neće, ocjene.

1296
00:44:16,620 --> 00:44:18,080
 Ocjene su pozitivne.

1297
00:44:18,080 --> 00:44:19,440
 Ima i negativnih.

1298
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:21,540
 Ne smijemo varati djecu.

1299
00:44:21,540 --> 00:44:23,020
 Ako je nešto za 1-1,

1300
00:44:23,020 --> 00:44:24,000
 ispravit će.

1301
00:44:24,200 --> 00:44:25,420
 Jelinica nekad može biti

1302
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:26,620
 strašna motivacija,

1303
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:27,220
 vjerujte mi.

1304
00:44:27,220 --> 00:44:28,680
 Možda, da.

1305
00:44:28,680 --> 00:44:29,340
 Strašna motivacija.

1306
00:44:29,340 --> 00:44:30,020
 Da se nauči za nešto.

1307
00:44:30,020 --> 00:44:30,980
 Nećemo djeca raditi

1308
00:44:30,980 --> 00:44:31,780
 da su savršena,

1309
00:44:31,780 --> 00:44:32,380
 briljantna.

1310
00:44:32,380 --> 00:44:33,780
 I kad dožive prvi neuspih,

1311
00:44:33,780 --> 00:44:35,360
 onda mi skaču sa zgrada.

1312
00:44:35,360 --> 00:44:37,480
 Tako da, nećemo varati djecu.

1313
00:44:37,480 --> 00:44:38,480
 Onako kako je,

1314
00:44:38,480 --> 00:44:38,980
 tako je.

1315
00:44:38,980 --> 00:44:40,660
 Evo, ako ima pitanja,

1316
00:44:40,660 --> 00:44:41,880
 rado ću odgovoriti.

1317
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:43,260
 Nadam se da neće

1318
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,480
 samo učenici nazvati

1319
00:44:44,480 --> 00:44:45,620
 da pitaju,

1320
00:44:45,620 --> 00:44:46,500
 sutra pitam.

1321
00:44:46,500 --> 00:44:48,500
 Evo, Dejane,

1322
00:44:48,500 --> 00:44:50,580
 je li imamo pitanja?

1323
00:44:50,580 --> 00:44:52,380
 Halo?

1324
00:44:53,820 --> 00:44:54,600
 Halo, halo?

1325
00:44:54,600 --> 00:44:55,580
 Mamo pitanja?

1326
00:44:55,580 --> 00:44:56,980
 Halo, leti, pozdrav.

1327
00:44:56,980 --> 00:44:57,860
 Dobar dan.

1328
00:44:57,860 --> 00:45:00,000
 Evo, ja vas pozdravljam.

1329
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:02,080
 O zim i sva u žitkom

1330
00:45:02,080 --> 00:45:04,860
 slušam vaše iskustva.

1331
00:45:04,860 --> 00:45:07,300
 Ja sam i to u obrazovanju,

1332
00:45:07,300 --> 00:45:09,500
 u razrednoj nastavi,

1333
00:45:09,500 --> 00:45:12,320
 i potpuno se slažem s vama.

1334
00:45:12,320 --> 00:45:14,440
 Vi ste mladi čovjek

1335
00:45:14,440 --> 00:45:16,560
 i možete još puno toga napraviti.

1336
00:45:17,280 --> 00:45:18,880
 Ja sam negdje pred odlaskom,

1337
00:45:18,880 --> 00:45:23,460
 ali mislim da mi trebamo,

1338
00:45:23,460 --> 00:45:24,960
 odnosno mi,

1339
00:45:24,960 --> 00:45:26,060
 ne mi,

1340
00:45:26,060 --> 00:45:30,220
 ali ja radim na jednoj specifičnoj ustanovi,

1341
00:45:30,220 --> 00:45:32,180
 mi probamo educirati roditelje

1342
00:45:32,180 --> 00:45:34,200
 o štetnosti ekrana za djecu.

1343
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:35,520
 E, to bi bilo super,

1344
00:45:35,520 --> 00:45:36,360
 da, to bi mogli.

1345
00:45:36,360 --> 00:45:38,240
 Pa mi imamo ono,

1346
00:45:38,240 --> 00:45:39,840
 sedam dana bez ekrana,

1347
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:42,360
 učimo roditelje u radionice i tako,

1348
00:45:42,360 --> 00:45:46,740
 jer mi smo svi sada izloženi

1349
00:45:46,740 --> 00:45:48,380
 tom što ste vi rekli,

1350
00:45:48,380 --> 00:45:50,300
 elektronici,

1351
00:45:50,300 --> 00:45:54,700
 ispravljam se ovoga.

1352
00:45:54,700 --> 00:45:57,420
 I mislim da mi roditelje sami nisu svjesni,

1353
00:45:57,420 --> 00:45:59,500
 ja sam jednu mamu pitala,

1354
00:45:59,500 --> 00:46:01,360
 djete ima problema strašni s koncentracijom

1355
00:46:01,360 --> 00:46:03,480
 u sve dodatne poteškoće,

1356
00:46:03,480 --> 00:46:06,260
 pa koliko je on dnevno vama na ekranu,

1357
00:46:06,340 --> 00:46:07,160
 da nije u skoli.

1358
00:46:07,160 --> 00:46:07,920
 Ona kaže,

1359
00:46:07,920 --> 00:46:09,540
 a ne, ne, nije puno,

1360
00:46:09,540 --> 00:46:10,760
 mi njega konsoliramo.

1361
00:46:10,760 --> 00:46:11,880
 Ja kažem, koliko je?

1362
00:46:11,880 --> 00:46:13,480
 Pa, četiri, pet sati.

1363
00:46:13,480 --> 00:46:15,380
 Jesu sam se šokirala.

1364
00:46:15,380 --> 00:46:17,040
 To je već ovisnik.

1365
00:46:17,040 --> 00:46:20,320
 Da, to je ovisnik o tehnologije već.

1366
00:46:20,320 --> 00:46:21,280
 Tako je.

1367
00:46:21,280 --> 00:46:23,620
 Roditelji nisu svjesni.

1368
00:46:23,620 --> 00:46:23,800
 Ne.

1369
00:46:23,800 --> 00:46:25,560
 Ovoga, ne znam,

1370
00:46:25,560 --> 00:46:26,940
 je li to vaše iskustvo?

1371
00:46:26,940 --> 00:46:28,540
 I mi sad pokušavamo,

1372
00:46:28,540 --> 00:46:30,200
 odnosno pokušavamo već dugo,

1373
00:46:30,200 --> 00:46:32,440
 biti tim raznim radionicama,

1374
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:33,740
 roditelje educirati,

1375
00:46:33,740 --> 00:46:35,440
 da roditeljima posvjesimo,

1376
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:38,660
 jer ne može dijete samo sebe odgajat.

1377
00:46:38,660 --> 00:46:38,940
 Je.

1378
00:46:38,940 --> 00:46:41,140
 U nekoj odrasloj dobi, ali.

1379
00:46:41,140 --> 00:46:43,180
 Da, ali sve više škola ukida mobitela,

1380
00:46:43,180 --> 00:46:44,880
 škola moja je jedna od tih.

1381
00:46:44,880 --> 00:46:46,160
 Da, tako da, evo,

1382
00:46:46,160 --> 00:46:47,880
 barem pola dana nisu bez mobitela,

1383
00:46:47,880 --> 00:46:49,100
 evo, to je prvi korak.

1384
00:46:49,100 --> 00:46:50,860
 Gledajte, ne može preko noći sve.

1385
00:46:50,860 --> 00:46:52,500
 To ćemo mi polako graditi.

1386
00:46:52,500 --> 00:46:53,460
 Ako imamo volje,

1387
00:46:53,460 --> 00:46:54,520
 ako ima volje,

1388
00:46:54,520 --> 00:46:55,320
 mi ćemo uspjeti.

1389
00:46:55,320 --> 00:46:56,100
 Ako nema volje,

1390
00:46:56,100 --> 00:46:57,340
 nek tipka i koliko go žele.

1391
00:46:58,020 --> 00:47:01,300
 Da, nažalost, ono, svi idemo

1392
00:47:01,300 --> 00:47:03,120
 i potpuno se s vama slažem da,

1393
00:47:03,120 --> 00:47:05,140
 evo, cijelo društvo treba

1394
00:47:05,140 --> 00:47:07,280
 dignuti razinu nas,

1395
00:47:07,280 --> 00:47:08,140
 učitelja,

1396
00:47:08,140 --> 00:47:11,460
 od plaće i sve te nepotrebne,

1397
00:47:11,460 --> 00:47:12,580
 kad vidimo troškove,

1398
00:47:12,580 --> 00:47:13,680
 to ste u pravu.

1399
00:47:14,680 --> 00:47:16,580
 treba dignuti nama ugled,

1400
00:47:16,580 --> 00:47:17,680
 da nas cijene,

1401
00:47:17,680 --> 00:47:19,100
 onda i roditelji,

1402
00:47:19,100 --> 00:47:19,900
 i djeca.

1403
00:47:19,900 --> 00:47:23,080
 Školstvo je, eto, tako kako je.

1404
00:47:23,080 --> 00:47:24,880
 Borimo se individualno

1405
00:47:24,880 --> 00:47:26,920
 i ja vam, ono, čestitam.

1406
00:47:26,920 --> 00:47:27,420
 Hvala.

1407
00:47:27,420 --> 00:47:29,540
 Želim vam svako dobro.

1408
00:47:29,540 --> 00:47:30,820
 Samo neke zdravlja, evo,

1409
00:47:30,820 --> 00:47:31,420
 bit će sve.

1410
00:47:31,420 --> 00:47:32,980
 Evo, tako je.

1411
00:47:32,980 --> 00:47:34,300
 Neka je zdravlja

1412
00:47:34,300 --> 00:47:36,980
 i, evo, nekim zajedničkim snagama

1413
00:47:36,980 --> 00:47:39,260
 i ovako kad čujem vas mlade

1414
00:47:39,260 --> 00:47:42,080
 i ovaj način kako vi radite,

1415
00:47:42,080 --> 00:47:43,300
 povezujete.

1416
00:47:43,920 --> 00:47:45,680
 znate što, ovoga,

1417
00:47:45,680 --> 00:47:48,220
 evo, meni koja sam pred mirovinom,

1418
00:47:48,220 --> 00:47:49,180
 pred odlaskom,

1419
00:47:49,180 --> 00:47:50,940
 nekako srce zaigra

1420
00:47:50,940 --> 00:47:52,600
 i, kažem, ono, ima nade.

1421
00:47:52,600 --> 00:47:54,380
 Je, hvala vam na riječima

1422
00:47:54,380 --> 00:47:55,920
 i pazite kako vozite.

1423
00:47:55,920 --> 00:47:57,380
 Za mladu djecu i za mlade

